sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant User as EndUser
    participant FE as ReactFrontend
    participant WAF as WAF
    participant Kong as Kong
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant IC as IntentClassifier
    participant OPA as OPA
    participant LLM as AIModels_LLM

    User->>FE: message + intent + JWT
    FE->>WAF: POST /api/ai/request (SSE)
    WAF->>Kong: forward
    Kong->>Kong: validate JWT
    Kong->>API: proxy with tenant headers
    API->>API: pre-flight security + PII
    API->>IC: resolve intent
    IC-->>API: intent label
    API->>OPA: policy check
    OPA-->>API: allow
    API->>LLM: stream request
    loop SSE tokens
        LLM-->>API: token
        API-->>FE: data: token
        FE-->>User: render stream
    end
    API->>API: persist usage + audit
